The CPU Detector 1.2.0 version is officially released, bringing a new experience. This update is as follows
● Fully adaptable to iOS 13, it is more convenient to use.
● Supports "dark mode" for low light environments (requires iOS 13 and above).
● Redesign the widget interface to make it clearer and more beautiful.
● Stability improvements and bug fixes.

CPU Detector 1.2.6版本正式發佈，帶來全新體驗，本次更新內容如下~
● 全面適配iOS 14，使用起來更順手。
● 支持"深色"模式，適用於弱光環境(要求iOS 13及以上)。
● 重新設計小組件界面，更加清晰美觀。
● 穩定性提升和錯誤修復。
